precis:
Amendment to the ABANDONMENT OF BRANCH LINES PROHIBITION ORDER NO. 16 which
withdraws the protection from abandonment affecting certain sections of
the following eight railway branch lines in Western Canada:
1. ROSSBURN (CN)  2. BODO (CN)  3. CENTRAL BUTTE (CN)  4. CUDWORTH (CN)
5. RIVERHURST (CN)  6. TONKIN (CN)  7. LYLETON (CP)  8. LANGDON (CP).
